FBIS3-41382 "jptdd008__l94090" JPRS-TDD-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 23 February 1994 EAST EUROPE BULGARIA Customs Seizes 6.65 Kg of Hashish on Greek Border AU1102165894 Sofia BTA in English 1513 GMT 11 Feb 94 AU1102165894 Sofia BTA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Blagoevgrad (southwestern Bulgaria), February 11 (BTA) -- Customs officers at the Kulata checkpoint (on the border with Greece) seized 6.650 kg of hashish yesterday. The narcotic was found in a handbag in a bus taking Bulgarian tourists to Greece. An investigation was launched and all passengers were questioned. A 27-year-old man admitted owning the handbag. Inquiry is under way.
